nodes.text: A flight of at least two BTL-B Y-wing starfighter/bombers of the Galactic Republic was active during the Clone Wars against the Confederacy of Independent Systems. The flight served as part of Clone Flight Squad Seven under the command of Clone Commander CC-2237. The flight participated in the Battle of Umbara, and bombed a ridge full of Umbaran Militia forces after they forced a battalion of the 501st Legion to retreat after calling in the airstrike.
